st of the UBER rogues you'll see on Rallos now were actualy started as twinks. If you are joining for PvP without good weapons and resist gear life is going to be very very tough all the way till 40s. If you do make it to 55+ you'll begin to shine in PvP <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uxyiin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xyiin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/11/02 8:51:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=580.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.envy.nu/xyiin/sepiroth.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sullon Zek or Rallos Zek</span><hr size=1> I've played a few nights on sullon. Got my wood elf rogue to lvl 7 for now... As many people have stated, it is extremely difficult to find groups. Even though i'm in Gfay, where there are usually 40-50 goodies, i can barely find even a partner to group with. If at low levels it's like this, i can't imagine the problems i may have in the higher levels. I've decided to stay on sullon, as rallos has gotten really boring. In TZ and VZ, people say it's constant politics, Immortal healing, Xteaming, blah blah blah. Well on RZ, in the low levels, there is no such thing as an even fight. Either your entire group gets demolished/pissed off bye ONE single Uber twink, or you are that uber twink pissing others off. I went up to like lvl 20 there, and i haven't had a decent battle of PVP which actually tested my skill. I think i'd be better off dueling people on a bluebie server. Well i'm sure SZ has a few qwerks (can't spell) of its own, but i'd much prefer it compared to the other three PVP servers. <p>-X-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unerezza.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nerezza</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/12/02 4:09:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=580.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sullon Zek or Rallos Zek</span><hr size=1> Well Xyiin, RZ has the least amount of pking twinks. Reason: item loot. No matter how twinked you are you will go low at some point and you know.. three hunder leather tunics that you looted do not replace one fungi that you lost when you went LD under attack. There are twinked low level pks guilds on Rallos but you can usualy see them from miles away as they tend to attack in groups and are known. Lone twink pks simply get ganked by classic naked caster teams, lose a couple of expensive items and quit out of frustration. TZ/VZ and to a degree SZ are perfect for twinking though, no item loot=level 20 rogue with 1500HPs, 12dmg+ pirecer, regeneration  and 30+ haste. <br>
